  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A creature with this ability causes disease in those it contacts. The effects of the disease, including its save, frequency, and cure, are included in the creature&rsquo;s description. The saving throw to negate the disease is usually a Fortitude save (DC = 10 + 1/2 infecting creature&rsquo;s racial HD + that creature&rsquo;s Constitution modifier; the exact DC is given in the creature&rsquo;s descriptive text). Diseases can be removed through <a class=\"entity-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; background-image: none; background-color: initial; padding: 0px; color: #ff6400; border: none;\" draggable=\"false\" data-pack=\"pf1.spells\" data-id=\"ocbjt6z7amc3yn8w\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; text-decoration-line: underline;\">remove disease</span></a> and similar effects.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em>Format</em>: <strong>Disease Name (Ex or Su)</strong> Bite&mdash;injury; <em>save</em> Fort DC 15, <em>onset</em> 1d3 days, <em>frequency</em> 1/day, <em>effect</em> 1 Con damage, <em>cure</em> 2 consecutive saves</p>\n<p><em>Location</em>: Special Attacks and individual attacks.</p>\n<p><em>Usage:&nbsp;</em>Replace Fort DC, and context</p>",
